//- Long identifiers (txids, addresses).
//-
//- Rows show the whole value where there is room and fall back to head…tail
//- below the 860px breakpoint, where a 64-char txid (384px) cannot fit a
//- phone's 324px of content. Both forms are emitted and swapped in CSS rather
//- than picking one server-side, so the choice can depend on viewport width;
//- the hidden one is display:none, which keeps it out of copy/paste.
//-
//- Not used by the homepage's two-column panels — a full txid needs 564px
//- there and the column is 472px.
mixin ident(full, short)
  span.ident-full= full
  span.ident-abbr= short
